<body>

<Header />

<!-- Breadcrumb Navigation -->
<nav class="breadcrumb" style="padding: 1rem 2rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #7a7a7a; background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e2e2;">
  <a href="/" style="color: #7a7a7a; text-decoration: none;">Home</a>
  <span style="margin: 0 0.5rem;">›</span>
  <span>Our Story</span>
</nav>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <h1>Built for <em>humans</em>, not lawyers.</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<main class="main-content">

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="content-inner">
      <h2>Why YourWillPro Exists</h2>
      <p>I was one of the 52% of Australians without a will.</p>
      <p>For years, I put it off. It felt morbid, complicated, and honestly — I didn't know where to start. Sound familiar?</p>
      <p>Then life changed. A new home. Growing responsibilities. People depending on me. Suddenly, not having a will wasn't just negligent — it was reckless.</p>
      <p>If something happened to me, the people I love most could be left in legal limbo, fighting for what should have been straightforward.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section alt">
    <div class="content-inner">
      <h2>The Problem with "Quick and Easy"</h2>
      <p>I looked at free and paid online wills. They promised simplicity. But they didn't answer my questions or explain why things mattered. They just asked me to fill in boxes.</p>
      <p>I had no idea if I was making the right choices — or setting my family up for problems down the track.</p>
      <p>That wasn't good enough. So I started digging.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="content-inner">
      <h2>What I Discovered</h2>
      <p>I spent months researching. I read court cases where families were torn apart by ambiguous wording. I learned how a single witness signature in the wrong place can invalidate an entire will.</p>
      <p>I discovered that superannuation doesn't automatically go where your will says — and most people don't know this.</p>
      <p>I found stories of executors overwhelmed by responsibilities they didn't understand. Of children left unprotected. Of wishes ignored because no one knew they existed.</p>
      <p>The more I learned, the more I realised how little most people understand about protecting their families.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section alt">
    <div class="content-inner">
      <h2>From Research to Resource</h2>
      <p>By the time I was ready to make my own will properly, I'd accumulated a mountain of information.</p>
      <p>And I thought: why should everyone else spend a year figuring this out?</p>
      <p>The information isn't hard to understand. It just takes time to find — buried in legal jargon, scattered across government websites, or locked behind expensive consultations.</p>
      <p>That's why I built YourWillPro. A free resource so you don't have to start from scratch like I did.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="content-inner">
      <h2>What This Site Offers</h2>
      <p>Everything here is free. Guides that explain the process step by step. Real stories showing what can go wrong — and what happens when families get it right.</p>
      <p>A dictionary of every term you'll encounter, written in plain English. Answers to the questions you're afraid to ask. Checklists to keep you on track.</p>
      <p>No sales pitch. No pressure. Just the information you need to protect the people who matter most.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content-section alt">
    <div class="content-inner">
      <h2>One Last Thing</h2>
      <p>I'm not a lawyer. This site doesn't replace legal advice for complex situations.</p>
      <p>But I am someone who's been exactly where you are — overwhelmed, unsure, and putting it off because it all felt too hard.</p>
      <p>If this site helps even one person avoid the mistakes that cost families so dearly, it's done its job.</p>
      <p>We'd love to hear from you. <a href="/feedback/">Send us feedback</a> or email <a href="mailto:contactus@yourwillpro.com.au">contactus@yourwillpro.com.au</a></p>
    </div>
  </section>

</main>

<Footer />

<style>
  /* Breadcrumb hover */
  .breadcrumb a:hover {
    color: #c9a227;
  }

  :root {
    --navy: #1a2e44;
    --gold: #c9a227;
    --gold-light: #faf6e9;
    --bg: #ffffff;
    --bg-light: #f7f8f9;
    --text-primary: #1a1a1a;
    --text-secondary: #4a4a4a;
    --border: #e2e2e2;
    --font-display: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    --font-body: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, sans-serif;
  }

  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--navy) 0%, #2a4560 100%);
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .hero h1 em {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* Main Content */
  .main-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-section {
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    background: var(--bg);
  }

  .content-section.alt {
    background: var(--bg-light);
  }

  .content-inner {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .content-section a {
    color: var(--navy);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .content-section a:hover {
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  /* Belief Items */
  .belief-item {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .belief-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .belief-item h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .belief-item p {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Offerings Grid */
  .offerings-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .offering-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .alt .offering-card {
    background: var(--bg-light);
  }

  .offering-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .offering-card h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .offering-card p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .content-section {
      padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .content-section p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .belief-item h3 {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }
  }
</style>

</body>
</html>
